sentences: Megumi Ogata (緒方 恵美, Ogata Megumi, born June 6, 1965) is a Japanese actress, voice actress and singer from the Greater Tokyo Area.
She married for the second time on April 1, 2004, and appeared with Ichirou Mizuki on NHK's second anime song marathon on April 30.
